If you control a "Galaxy-Eyes Tachyon Dragon" monster, you can activate this card from your hand.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Activate this card only if you currently control no Special Summoned monsters. While a monster is face-up on the field, negate its effects during the turn that monster was Special Summoned. If an Effect Monster(s) is Special Summoned in Attack Position: Change it to Defense Position.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Banish your opponent's entire hand, and if you do, they draw the same number of cards. You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 "Trickstar" monster in your GY; Special Summon it.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Each player can only control 1 monster of each Type. If a player controls 2 or more monsters of the same Type, they must send some to the GY so they control no more than 1 monster of that Type.
